snippet.title: Dead Cells - Mobile Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Kill. Die. Learn. Repeat. This summer, the indie hit Dead Cells will slay its way to iOS devices!
Pre-order it now on iOS: http://bit.ly/DeadCells_iOS
Get notified when it's out for iOS and later for Android: https://playdigious.com/dead-cells/

Learn more about the game: https://playdigious.com/dead-cells/
Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/playdigious
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/playdigious
Join us on Discord: https://discord.gg/ZyUHpTd
